Lil Tim, but make it Hard-Core 💪

Anything is almost possible if you put good intentions, authenticity, determination, focus, drive, and kindness behind it. The last two months have been less than easy from a personal, professional, and spiritual standpoint — I have felt attacked, unbalanced, scared, and in pain *(ask me privately, I could use a chat). One thing is for certain, discomfort, uncertainty, and negativity is only temporary for those of us who love everyday hard-core.

I’m keeping my chin up, the eyes on the prize, and moving on from ______ (insert all these shitty feels I’ve allowed into my life) - reclaiming my power starts with letting go.

More news to come soon - keep in touch with me for the full scoop 🙌

🌈🌟Love is in the air on Lincoln Road!🌟🌈 The Lincoln Road Business Improvement District @lincolnrd has transformed into Rainbow Road in honor of @miamibeachpride 's 15th Anniversary!🎉🏳️‍🌈 Snap a photo at one or all of the Rainbow Road locations and show your support for the LGBTQ+ community by using the hashtag #LoveOnLincoln.💕 All tagged photos will become a part of an epic collage to be presented in June during international #pridemonth 🙌

Plus, there's exciting programming to celebrate Pride all throughout April! Don't miss out on @casper 's 15% off promotion from March 31 to April 16, @7forallmankind 's extra 25% off offer, @jomalonelondon 's 15% off deal with custom rainbow blooming bouquets on April 1, @maccosmetics pride makeup glow-up on April 15 & 16, and @nespressousa 's special recipe at 20% off with a happy hour event on April 13th from 5 to 7 PM at their To Go Bar.🎉

Kick off with us as we "Light the Night" on March 31st, 2023, at the Euclid Oval 600-700 Lincoln Road, followed by a Pride Flag raising (7:30 PM) to pay tribute to the victims and families affected by the Pulse Nightclub and Club Q shootings.💔✨

Lincoln Road is the place to be with 200 restaurants and shops, arts and cultural offerings, and entertainment.👀💃 It's where models walk their dogs, stylish boulevardiers stroll past window shoppers, and café culture overrules standard business meetings. Join us in celebrating love, diversity, and inclusion with the #LoveOnLincoln campaign!💖

💖 Happy Mother’s Day, @lmtuggy! 💐

To the woman who radiates love, strength, and unwavering kindness, we celebrate the incredible mother you are. Your selflessness, compassion, and boundless devotion touch our lives in beautiful ways. 🌸

In your warm embrace, we find comfort and reassurance. Your nurturing spirit guides us through life’s challenges. You’re our rock, our confidante, and our biggest cheerleader. ✨

Your love knows no limits, and your sacrifices are immeasurable. You put our needs above your own, ensuring we thrive. You’re our superhero. 🌟

Through life’s highs and lows, you celebrate our triumphs and wipe away our tears. Your wisdom is our guiding light. Your belief in us fuels our dreams. 🌈

You’re not only our mother but also our best friend. Your infectious joy brightens our lives. Your presence is a gift we cherish. 🌺

Today, we honor the extraordinary woman you are. Your beautiful soul shines through in everything you do. We are blessed to call you our mom. ❤️

Wishing all incredible mothers a Happy Mother’s Day! May your hearts be filled with joy and know how deeply you are loved and appreciated. ❤️🌸❤️

#MothersLove #UnconditionalLove #MomIsMyWorld #HappyMothersDay

Embracing Simplicity and Grateful for My Body's Wisdom ✨💖

🌿 Sometimes life reminds us to slow down and appreciate the beauty of simplicity. Today, I find myself cherishing the little things and truly listening to my body's messages. As my right knee and left ankle heal, I am reminded of the incredible strength and resilience my body possesses. 🙏💪

🌟 It's during these moments of stillness that I realize how important it is to be present, to connect with our bodies, and to tune into the universe's whispers. The universe has a way of guiding us, and when we listen closely, it never steers us wrong. ✨🌌

Slow down, breathe deeply, and appreciate the effortless beauty that surrounds us every day. 🌸🌱
